The paper discusses bug bounties and the disclosure of web vulnerabilities, which are topics related to computer security (cs.CR) and software engineering (cs.SE). The paper also touches on the use of automated tools for vulnerability discovery, which falls under the category of cyber-physical systems (cs.CY). The discussion of platform economy and vulnerability markets relates to social and information networks (cs.SI) and distributed, parallel, and cluster computing (cs.DC).
